&gt;&gt;That one works in a pinch but not exactly amazing.<br>
<br>
Yes we do get another lvl63 spell Deaths peace (30 second) up to lvl 59 mobs. (havent tested out the max level yet, having trouble finding a lvl65 undead mob)<br>
<br>
All necros have an aversion of mana dumping someone else since if they give mana to a wizard its considered a waste (necros do the same damage with that mana). giving it to a sk for pulling a waste too since the necro can pull just as well. To a healer waste since necro can heal (here I actually dont care since my heals are gimpy, would much rather a priest do the healing, that is if the priest is not constantly lom).<br>
<br>
Yes necros can generate high damage and with that comes high aggro, to counter that they have a spell named freign death or deaths peace that allows to drop the aggro again.<br>
<br>
What people have to keep in mind that mana dumpin is not cheap eg takes 400 mana away from you and gives 150 mana to the target. <br>
<br>
Trying to do that in an xp group is simply not going to work, necro will be oom almost constantly by twitch, so sitting on your butt waiting to get mana just to give to someone, now what fun is that. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sulissaurnvelve>Sulissa UrnVelve</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Almost dangerous<br>
