I think the problem the original posted aludes to comes from 2 aspects.<br>
<br>
1. many necros solo most of their careers, so at high levels when fear is no longer an option, they join groups and need to adjust or aren't familiar with what they can contribute.<br>
<br>
2. same cause, other consequence, many people don't have necros in their groups so they don't learn what they can bring to it, and so learn it at higher levels.<br>
